---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About | Wildlife">
  <div class="page-hero">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <h1>About</h1>
      <p>A conservation photography project</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <article class="about-article">
    <div class="article-content">
      <p class="lead">This book is a celebration of Earth's wildlife and a call to conservation action. Through AI-generated photography and carefully researched text, we explore the magnificent creatures that share our planet.</p>

      <h2>The Concept</h2>
      <p>The idea for this project emerged from a simple question: How can we use modern technology to celebrate and document wildlife in new ways? AI image generation has reached a point where it can create photorealistic images that capture the essence and beauty of animals—images that serve not as replacements for wildlife photography, but as complements that allow us to explore scenes and moments that would be impossible or unethical to capture in the wild.</p>

      <h2>Seven Continents</h2>
      <p>Each continent tells a unique story of evolution, adaptation, and survival. From the elephants of Africa to the penguins of Antarctica, the animals featured in this book represent the incredible diversity of life on Earth.</p>

      <h2>Conservation</h2>
      <p>Every animal profile includes conservation status and the threats each species faces. Awareness is the first step toward action. Many of the species featured here are endangered or vulnerable—not because they're not magnificent enough to survive, but because human activities have made their survival difficult.</p>

      <blockquote>
        "In the end, we will conserve only what we love, we will love only what we understand, and we will understand only what we are taught."
        <cite>— Baba Dioum</cite>
      </blockquote>

      <h2>Technology</h2>
      <p>The images in this book were created using AI image generation models, with prompts carefully crafted to produce photorealistic wildlife photography. Each image was generated with attention to anatomical accuracy, natural lighting, and environmental context.</p>

      <h2>Ethics</h2>
      <p>AI-generated wildlife images raise interesting questions about authenticity and representation. This project uses AI not to deceive, but to create art that celebrates wildlife. Every image is clearly identified as AI-generated, and the focus remains on education and conservation awareness.</p>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>

<style>
  .page-hero {
    height: 50vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    text-align: center;
    background: #050505;
    position: relative;
  }

  .page-hero::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse at center, #0f0f0f 0%, #050505 70%);
  }

  .hero-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    padding: 2rem;
  }

  .hero-content h1 {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3rem);
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: white;
  }

  .hero-content p {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.35);
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .about-article {
    max-width: 650px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 4rem 2rem 6rem;
  }

  .article-content .lead {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  .article-content h2 {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    margin: 3rem 0 1rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
  }

  .article-content p {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45);
  }

  .article-content blockquote {
    margin: 3rem 0;
    padding: 1.5rem 0;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .article-content blockquote cite {
    display: block;
    margin-top: 0.75rem;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
    font-style: normal;
  }
</style>
